  "title": "Assistant Senior Social Worker @ Hougang Sheng Hong Family Service Centre",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Key Responsibility Areas</strong></u></p>\n<p>- Casework and counselling</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide casework management to clients with varying needs, risk and safety concerns.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with internal and external stakeholders to achieve case plan outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Keep track of rising trends and patterns, develop interventions and programmes within the organisation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>- Group Work/ Community Work</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead/ Co-lead group work to target client groups or other stakeholders/ agencies.</li>\n  <li>Lead/ Co-lead initiatives on community development.</li>\n  <li>Ensure programme outcomes are met.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>- Supervision</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide supervision to at least 4 supervisees on casework and counselling.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>- Perform other duties as assigned by the Assistant Director (Head of FSC).</p>\n<p><u><strong>Required qualifications and experience</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree, Graduate Diploma or Master in Social Work / Degree or Master in Counselling.</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 4-6 years experience in a Social Service Agency with at least 1 year of supervisory experience. Current experience in Family Service Centre is an added advantage.</li>\n  <li>Good report writing skill.</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Good organisational skill.</li>\n</ul>",
